</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BE98519D10D496D79C3C7F7FBC532B5" blockId="20.[189,1086,1720,1747]" box="[189,1086,1720,1747]" pageId="20" pageNumber="77">Baltic amber is considered to be of Bartonian–Priabonian age, ca 34–38 Ma.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
